Paper: hep-th/9510094

Date: 1995-10-14

Title: Natural gauge-coupling unification at the string scale

Comments: 5 pages, LaTeX file. Minor modifications, final version to appear in

Physics Letters BJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B370 (1996) 49-51

We argue that moduli in the adjoint representation of the standard- modelgauge group are a natural feature of superstring models, and that they canaccount for the apparent discrepancy between the string and unification scales.